144
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,800
As long as you absorb its soul power,

145
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,960
not only will your third soul skill be improved,

146
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:48,480
you will also have a defensive fourth soul skill.

147
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:50,160
Master. To me,

148
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:53,560
the Burrow Demon Spider is
more useful to me now.

149
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:56,600
Why?

150
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,640
Master, I picked it because

151
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,800
the Advanced Soul Master
School Contest is coming soon.

152
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:03,180
If you have time to think of that,

153
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:05,100
you should think about yourself!

154
00:15:05,100 --> 00:15:08,080
It’s 5,000 years way above your league.

155
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:11,920
Do you think you can absorb it completely?

156
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:14,960
Master, believe me. I can do it.

157
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:18,540
I consumed two premium herbs
when I was at the Old Freak’s place.

158
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:22,980
They have changed my body completely.

159
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:26,400
I’m way stronger than you think.

160
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:29,160
And I have an advantage here too.

161
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:31,540
The two premium herbs that I have consumed,

162
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:33,220
allow me to absorb the soul ring

163
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:35,500
in a special place.

164
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:36,640
With all that,

165
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:40,560
I’m confident that I can absorb its power.

166
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:43,240
Xiao Wu.

167
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:45,260
Even if you’re 99% sure of it,

168
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,920
I won’t let you take the risk.

169
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,700
Decade Millennium Soul Beasts

170
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:51,040
