And it’ll be very hard for you.

174
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:01,040
Soul shock? What’s that?

175
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:04,260
It’s a phenomenon where
powerful soul beasts produce

176
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:07,240
special energy before
their souls disappears completely.

177
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:09,700
Only Decade Millennium Soul Beasts
can cause soul shock.

178
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:13,720
Soul shock will destroy a person’s mentality.

179
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:16,460
And it will cause that person to become an idiot.

180
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,920
Xiao Wu, how did you know all that?

181
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:24,200
My mother told me that.

182
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:27,140
Soul shock?

183
00:16:27,140 --> 00:16:30,780
Brother, you said you would
protect me forever, right?

184
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:33,520
I beg you, please listen to Grandmaster.

185
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:36,660
That Human-Faced Demon Spider is not bad too.

186
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:40,180
Why must you take the risk?

187
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:42,660
What if I can avoid soul shock?

188
00:16:42,660 --> 00:16:43,980
Brother!

189
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:57,780
Did you forget about the Eager Gaze Dew
that I consumed?

190
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,460
With the Purple Demon Eye,

191
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:00,880
I’m sure

192
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:05,260
